ions and industries these include the automotive industry power generation aviation and certain niches in the industrial market such as refrigeration and grease learn more • anderol brand specialty lubricantspetroleum additives’ anderol unit is a leading manufacturer and marketer of high performance specialty lubricants used in wide ranging industrial applications backed by over  years of experience anderol has a pedigree of technological leadership pioneering the use of synthetic fluids in aviation learn more • hatco brand polyol esterspetroleum additives’ hatco unit is the world’s premier producer of polyol esters these esters are used as basestocks in the production of ultra high performance lubricants for aviation automotive and industrial applications learn more urethanes chemturas urethanes business is a world leader in hotcast prepolymers and a leading manufacturer of specialty aqueous urethane dispersions and polyester polyols the business is characterized by a strong customer focus exceptional product and applications development capability and outstanding technical service learn more • rubber labelschemtura has been producing vulcanizable rubber labels for more than  years these custom labels are an effective and economical way to stimulate initial purchases of your product and boost sales volume learn more • adiprene ®we offer more than  hotcast urethane prepolymer products under the adiprene®vibrathane®duracast® brand names the product range includes a wide variety of wear and abrasion resistant cast elastomers that are recognized worldwide for their toughness loadbearing capacity and cut and tear resistance learn more industrial engineered productsgreat lakes solutions great lakes solutions is the flame retardants brominated performance products and fumigants business of chemtura – providing materials and services for use in electronics electrical building and construction fine chemicals agriculture power generation transportation water treatment oil refining and more  learn more organometallics specialties chemtura organometallics core competency is the production and safe handling of selected reactive organometallic products the combination of  years of operation and innovative development excellence with our global supply chain capabilities are the basis for a sustainable customer oriented business model learn more • daystar materialsdaystar materials specializes in hightech organometallics including those used for chemical vapor deposition in the manufacture of highbrightness leds learn more   brands ⁄ businesses anderol great lakes solutions hatco organometallics petroleum additives urethanes  chemtura adiprenevibrathane  products you may be trying to access this site from a secured browser on the server please enable scripts and reload this page turn on more accessible mode turn off more accessible mode skip ribbon commands skip to main content turn off animations turn on animations sign in chemtura adiprenevibrathane  products   recent north america region europelatin americaasia pacific español  português  it looks like your browser does not have javascript enabled please turn on javascript and try again home about usproductscurrently selectedmarkets and applicationslibrary page content products welcome to the adiprene®vibrathane®duracast® product finder please use the dropdown menus below to locate information on our adiprene®vibrathane®duracast® products if you would prefer to search for a product by name please use the search box at the top of the page search prepolymers search type blocked prepolymer duracast conventional prepolymer lf prepolymer quasi prepolymer isocyanatetype tdi isocyanate mdi isocyanate hdi isocyanate ppdi isocyanate hmdi isocyanate polyoltype ether polyol polycaprolactone polyol ester polyol polycarbonate polyol hardnessrange a  d d  d a  a a  a a  a d  d d  d ≥ d ≤ a a  d search curatives search type diol curative amine curative related links msds product finder products adiprene