 ideal for use in low temperature applications down to ˚cthe pseries elastomers are designed for the most demanding applications they offer superior toughness excellent dynamic properties and can perform consistently at elevated temperatures up to ˚c and in harsh chemical environmentsthe hseries elastomers provide excellent weatherability uv resistance and color retention while offering high rebound toughness with high cut and tear resistance and low temperature performanceproducts product familyultralast® tpudescription mseries polyetherm me me me med superior dynamic performance and resistance to hydrolysis available in ad mseries polycaprolactone mc superior dynamic performance and toughness available in a mseries polycarbonate mr superior toughness and performance in harsh environments available in a pseries polyether pe pe pe superior dynamic performance toughness and high rebound available in ad pseries polycaprolactone pcm superior dynamic performance toughness and low compression set available in a pseries polycarbonate pr pr prd superior toughness and hydrolysis chemical and oil resistance at high temperatures available in ad hseries polyether he superior toughness low temperature performance and excellent weatherability available in a chemtura adiprene fomrez witcobond contact us privacy policy terms of use  chemtura corporation all rights reserved chemtura corporation sa de cv  supplier  colombia  import genius plans limited plus premium limitedmonitor your competitors data access data on us ocean freight imports from the last  months for all companies youll have access to data from the previous months from the date of your search we use a rolling date range so you can always look back  months from the current date limitedmonitor your competitors data access data on us ocean freight imports from the last  months for all companies access data on us ocean freight imports from the last  months for all companies youll have access to data from the previous mon