 detergents emulsifiers epantiwear finished lubricants fuel additives grease intermediates phenolic antioxidants phosphites synthetic basestocks aminic antioxidants antioxidants are vital components in the prevention of lubricant oxidative degradation due to exposure to oxygen heat light and metals during storage and service products   naugalube®  ​naugalube®  provides excellent oxidation stability in a wide range of petroleum products and is especially effective as an antioxidant in fuels and with vegetable oil based lubricants technical data sheet naugalube® l ​naugalube® l is a nonylated diphenylamine for use as an antioxidant in mineral and synthetic base stocks that are typically employed in lubricant applications its liquid form allows for easy handling and blending naugalube l can easily be incorporated into engine oils gear oils hydraulic fluids turbine oils and greases technical data sheet naugalube®  ​naugalube®  is an octylated butylated diphenylamine antioxidant for use in mineral and synthetic base stocks that are typically employed in lubricant applications its high nitrogen content and liquid form allows for incorporation into high performance passenger car and diesel engine oils automatic transmission fluids marine diesel oils industrial oils and greases technical data sheet naugalube®  ​naugalube® is a lowvolatility alkylated diphenylamine antioxidant which provides excellent oxidation stability to mineral oils and synthetic fluids its features include low volatility clear reddish color and a high nitrogen content naugalube  has shown applicability in passenger car engine oils aviation turbine oils and industrial oils technical data sheet naugalube®  ​naugalube  is a mixed butyl octyl diphenylamine antioxidant for use in lubricants formulated with mineral and synthetic base stocks technical data sheetnaugalube  commercial naugalube® ams ​naugalube® ams is a high molecular weight amine antioxidant which provides excellent oxidation stability to both mineral oils and synthetic fluids  naugalube ams has show applicability in automatic transmission fluids diesel engine oils and industrial oils technical data sheet naugalube® apan ​naugalube® apan is a powerful long lasting low sludging antioxidant which provides excellent stability in a wide range of petroleum products it is especially cost effective antioxidant in service applications for turbine oils compressor oils and hydraulic oils where low color and longevity is desired technical data sheet naugalube® tmq ​naugalube® tmq is an especially effective antioxidant in ester containing fluids and grease formulations it can be easily incorporated into gear oils turbine oils hydraulic fluids compressor oils and greases technical data sheet naugard® pana ​naugard® pana phenylalphanaphthylamine is an excellent antioxidant for synthetic fluids and mineral oils it is particularly useful in high temperature applications such as aviation turbine engine oils and in the formulation of high performance industrial oils and greases technical data sheet   products  services applications contacts news  events about us   home chemturacom privacy contact sitemap legal msds request   chemtura corporation all rights reserved microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicro